0:02:23.360,0:02:24.713
What a clever woman.

0:02:26.550,0:02:27.520
Do you know...

0:02:28.503,0:02:29.979
what I would do...

0:02:31.000,0:02:32.243
to a clever woman?

0:02:34.000,0:02:35.000
You'd kill me?

0:02:35.800,0:02:37.440
Unfortunately, the Dzungars would never

0:02:37.440,0:02:38.640
kill someone who saves them.

0:02:41.310,0:02:43.020
I have no intention of killing you.

0:02:44.610,0:02:45.812
A clever woman

0:02:46.720,0:02:48.480
who is beautiful at the same time...

0:02:50.720,0:02:53.480
can easily be an object of desire.

0:02:53.880,0:02:54.880
Sir,

0:02:55.400,0:02:56.880
your remarks are out of line.

0:02:59.580,0:03:00.960
We Dzungars...

0:03:01.313,0:03:03.950
are not shy about what we like.

0:03:05.400,0:03:06.733
When we fancy a thing,

0:03:07.800,0:03:10.760
we do everything we can to acquire it.

0:03:18.360,0:03:19.360
Don't forget...

0:03:19.800,0:03:21.875
This is the land of the Great Qing.

0:03:31.773,0:03:33.068
The day may come

0:03:34.092,0:03:36.640
when this land becomes the territory of the Dzungars.

0:03:40.480,0:03:42.195
We saved your life just now.

0:03:43.040,0:03:44.800
But we can kill you just as easily.

0:03:46.520,0:03:47.540
Can you?

0:03:49.200,0:03:50.560
It wouldn't be so easy.

0:03:52.180,0:03:55.340
In the past, at least your country had Nian Gengyao.

0:03:56.720,0:03:58.000
But now,

0:03:58.800,0:04:01.120
you don't have a single competent general.

0:04:02.980,0:04:04.970
You're less capable than a runaway soldier.

0:04:07.320,0:04:09.155
I don't think you're worthy of my concern.

0:04:09.720,0:04:10.720
You're lucky

0:04:12.640,0:04:14.524
because I will not harm an injured man.

0:04:20.160,0:04:21.160
Sir!

0:04:21.680,0:04:22.875
Sir! Sir!

0:04:24.460,0:04:25.450
Sir! Sir!

0:04:26.720,0:04:27.720
Sir!

0:04:27.920,0:04:29.630
It was so hard to find you.

0:04:30.160,0:04:31.210
What happened?

0:04:32.280,0:04:33.280
I was...

0:04:34.400,0:04:36.130
bitten by a poisonous snake up the hill.

0:04:37.760,0:04:39.560
Luckily they saved me.

0:04:44.480,0:04:45.799
Thank you very much, sir,

0:04:46.013,0:04:47.310
and the two ladies,

0:04:47.571,0:04:48.715
for saving My Lord.

0:04:49.240,0:04:51.518
You should be more careful going out in the future.

0:04:52.440,0:04:53.476
The next time,

0:04:53.476,0:04:55.760
you might not be so lucky to leave unscathed.

0:04:57.660,0:04:59.360
That's very caring of you.

0:05:00.000,0:05:01.000
It may seem so,

0:05:01.200,0:05:04.000
but only because you value your own life.

0:05:05.800,0:05:07.222
To use a phrase from your language ...

0:05:08.640,0:05:10.583
you could be considered almost a soul mate of mine.

0:05:12.000,0:05:13.750
You said that as a compliment,

0:05:14.000,0:05:15.680
but it will be my life-long fortune

0:05:15.720,0:05:17.280
to never again see your lordly face.

0:05:17.920,0:05:18.920
Please suit yourself.

0:05:23.520,0:05:24.600
Here, master.

0:05:25.310,0:05:26.800
Let's go, master.

0:05:27.480,0:05:28.480
Be careful.

0:05:32.200,0:05:33.200
Good.

0:05:33.400,0:05:34.400
Thank you.

0:05:36.520,0:05:37.520
Take it slow.

0:05:43.750,0:05:44.720
Let's go.

0:05:51.200,0:05:52.520
Why did you bring so many books?

0:05:52.520,0:05:53.623
Where are they from?

0:05:54.340,0:05:57.520
I boldly asked His Lordship for some books.

0:05:57.800,0:05:59.600
He sent Ajin to deliver these today.

0:06:00.320,0:06:02.840
It is enough for me to read 
my few books for leisure.

0:06:03.120,0:06:05.000
Why did you ask him for so many?

0:06:06.350,0:06:07.810
My Lady, can you teach me literary classics?

0:06:09.860,0:06:12.000
But you've never been interested in poetry and prose.

0:06:12.520,0:06:14.240
What changed your mind?

0:06:15.860,0:06:17.920
Isn't it good for me to know more about literature?

0:06:19.030,0:06:20.560
My Lady, you've always had a passion for reading.

0:06:20.950,0:06:22.400
If I can understand literature better,

0:06:22.606,0:06:24.371
I can help relieve your boredom.

0:06:25.750,0:06:27.490
My Lady, you have His Lordship now,

0:06:27.720,0:06:29.778
and you two are like a couple in a fairy tale.

0:06:30.400,0:06:32.200
But can't I keep you company as well?

0:06:34.520,0:06:35.889
Don't sidestep the real issue.

0:06:36.320,0:06:37.403
Let me ask you,

0:06:37.800,0:06:39.560
when I was composing poetry with him a few days ago,

0:06:39.800,0:06:41.290
you heard us, didn't you?

0:06:44.310,0:06:45.600
Since you have figured me out,

0:06:46.440,0:06:47.720
I won't hide it anymore.

0:06:50.400,0:06:51.920
My Lady, you and His Lordship are so knowledgeable

0:06:52.560,0:06:54.240
and fluently hold intelligent conversations all day.

0:06:55.000,0:06:56.638
Yet I don't understand anything.

0:06:57.640,0:06:58.640
The other day...

0:06:58.880,0:07:02.020
when I heard how beautifully
you two composed poetry together,

0:07:03.000,0:07:05.880
I stood as dumb as a piece of wood.

0:07:06.480,0:07:07.885
I couldn't be more ashamed.

0:07:09.370,0:07:11.960
Wishing to improve oneself is a most desirable trait.

0:07:12.310,0:07:13.760
As long as you're willing to learn,

0:07:13.760,0:07:15.685
I'm always happy to teach you.

0:07:16.880,0:07:18.366
It's just that...

0:07:18.366,0:07:20.526
the more a woman reads and learns,

0:07:20.800,0:07:23.670
the more melancholy and wistful she may feel.

0:07:24.280,0:07:25.600
But that's still better

0:07:26.080,0:07:27.590
than being ignorant and senseless.

0:07:47.400,0:07:49.720
Please request My Lady to come out 
to receive His Majesty's decree.

0:07:49.720,0:07:50.720
Mr. Su,

0:07:50.880,0:07:52.920
you don't know My Lady's personality.

0:07:52.920,0:07:54.720
She's intractable like an untamed horse.

0:07:55.160,0:07:57.400
She's training a horse right now.

0:07:58.000,0:08:00.000
She will definitely not come out.

0:08:00.560,0:08:01.750
If you wait for her here,

0:08:01.880,0:08:03.520
it could be four to six hours.

0:08:03.880,0:08:06.000
Can your task be delayed so long?

0:08:06.400,0:08:07.800
My goodness!

0:08:08.000,0:08:09.840
She can afford to wait, but I can't.

0:08:10.160,0:08:11.920
I need to get back to attend to His Majesty.

0:08:12.120,0:08:13.120
Mr. Su,

0:08:13.120,0:08:14.400
I know you're afraid of horses...

0:08:14.800,0:08:15.800
But don't worry —

0:08:15.800,0:08:17.360
even though the horse is wild by nature,

0:08:17.680,0:08:19.280
it definitely won't hurt you

0:08:19.520,0:08:21.614
while My Lady is present.

0:08:23.600,0:08:26.320
Your Majesty, why have you taken a liking to this one?

0:08:29.640,0:08:32.320
My Lady, you've finally come 
to receive His Majesty's decree.

0:08:32.880,0:08:34.004
Say what you have to.

0:08:35.120,0:08:36.326
By His Majesty's decree...

0:08:41.120,0:08:42.300
I apologize, My Lady,

0:08:42.560,0:08:44.083
but you must kneel to receive the decree.

0:08:49.100,0:08:51.340
By the Grace of Heaven, His Majesty decrees:

0:08:51.546,0:08:54.310
“Ye from the Summer Palace has 
a keen intellect and an elegant manner."

0:08:54.320,0:08:57.000
"She is awarded the title of Companion 
and will be relocated to the palace."

0:08:57.160,0:08:58.201
This is His Majesty's edict.

0:09:07.360,0:09:08.360
My Lady,

0:09:08.440,0:09:09.740
you need to thank His Majesty.

0:09:11.480,0:09:12.480
Thanks.

0:09:14.560,0:09:15.864
Congratulations, Lady Ye.

0:09:16.480,0:09:17.790
How fortunate you are!

0:09:18.160,0:09:21.480
Palace servants usually start from the rank of Escort.

0:09:21.600,0:09:23.800
But you've leapt to the rank of Companion.

0:09:25.120,0:09:26.680
Do you want this kind of fortune?

0:09:26.680,0:09:28.040
My Lady, you must be joking!

0:09:28.040,0:09:29.080
Must be joking!

0:09:30.430,0:09:32.920
Please pack up and get ready for the move.

0:09:34.920,0:09:36.370
Where will I live in the palace?

0:09:36.370,0:09:37.640
The Household Department will take care of it.

0:09:37.920,0:09:40.000
The Household Department has their own work to do.

0:09:40.294,0:09:41.440
Since His Majesty likes me,

0:09:41.440,0:09:43.247
why would he let the Household Department 
arrange this for me?

0:09:43.960,0:09:45.310
I don't like noise.

0:09:45.680,0:09:47.190
Please tell His Majesty

0:09:47.400,0:09:49.600
to settle me in a remote and quiet place.

0:09:49.960,0:09:50.995
Yes,

0:09:50.995,0:09:52.691
His Majesty will certainly arrange that for you.

0:09:52.920,0:09:54.820
My Lady, please hurry.

0:09:55.480,0:09:57.280
You still need to thank His Majesty in person.

0:09:59.000,0:10:00.800
I won't be able to wait until he comes.

0:10:00.800,0:10:02.560
I promised him a performance.

0:10:03.000,0:10:04.400
My Lady, who are you talking about?

0:10:04.920,0:10:06.000
None of your business.

0:10:14.680,0:10:15.760
Look at this fish.

0:10:16.000,0:10:17.880
Its eyes are bulging out.

0:10:20.000,0:10:21.124
This one looks pretty.

0:10:22.120,0:10:24.720
Peace to Your Majesty the Empress Dowager. 
Peace to Your Majesty the Empress.

0:10:25.156,0:10:26.440
Peace to Your Highness Concubine Astuce.

0:10:27.320,0:10:28.320
Rise.

0:10:28.320,0:10:29.320
I thank Your Majesty.

0:10:31.640,0:10:34.205
I appreciate you taking time from your busy schedule.

0:10:34.600,0:10:35.610
It's my pleasure.

0:10:36.250,0:10:38.284
Although arrangements have been made discreetly,

0:10:39.000,0:10:41.641
she will be living in a palace sooner or later.

0:10:43.040,0:10:45.484
How long did the Emperor think he could hide it from me?

0:10:47.840,0:10:48.912
Let me ask you,

0:10:49.520,0:10:50.958
has the new concubine entered the palace?

0:10:51.720,0:10:52.926
What new concubine?

0:10:52.926,0:10:54.384
Why don't I know about it?

0:10:55.600,0:10:58.010
Because of your high virtue and gentle temperament,

0:10:58.200,0:11:00.160
the emperor believes that you would never oppose him.

0:11:00.760,0:11:03.284
So he has no scruples about bringing 
any woman into the palace.

0:11:04.720,0:11:06.025
Please don't be angry, Your Majesty.

0:11:06.320,0:11:08.840
She might be coming from a humble background.

0:11:09.280,0:11:13.400
Just like Lady Melodic, who was a palace servant.

0:11:14.200,0:11:15.200
At worst,

0:11:15.200,0:11:20.235
she could be a slave like the mother of Lord VIII.

0:11:20.440,0:11:24.126
Even a member of the slave caste 
was born to slaves who served officials.

0:11:25.440,0:11:28.927
The Emperor chose a multitalented woman this time -

0:11:29.600,0:11:33.323
a horse trainer from the stables in the Summer Palace.

0:11:34.720,0:11:35.808
Your Majesty,

0:11:36.400,0:11:38.080
she has already entered the palace.

0:11:38.800,0:11:40.970
His Majesty was concerned about her day and night

0:11:41.000,0:11:43.200
while she was still in the Summer Palace.

0:11:43.560,0:11:46.166
So His Majesty granted her the rank of Companion 
and moved her to the palace.

0:11:46.800,0:11:48.209
Has it been decided where to place her?

0:11:48.209,0:11:49.080
Not yet.

0:11:49.520,0:11:51.520
But Companion Ye has told me that

0:11:51.768,0:11:54.571
she prefers a quiet and secluded place.

0:11:55.240,0:11:56.452
Listen to this.

0:11:56.880,0:11:59.720
She is making demands even before
 moving into the palace!

0:12:00.760,0:12:01.760
Exactly.

0:12:02.360,0:12:04.332
Has the emperor made a decision on her residence?

0:12:04.332,0:12:06.920
The Household Department needs several days 
to clean and prepare the rooms.

0:12:07.360,0:12:10.320
His Majesty said she could live in the side chamber
of the Hall of Mental Cultivation for now.

0:12:10.320,0:12:11.320
That can't happen!

0:12:14.040,0:12:15.200
You tell the emperor that

0:12:15.800,0:12:18.320
the Hall of Spring Joy behind the
 Palace of Longevity is unoccupied.

0:12:18.840,0:12:20.800
Have it cleaned for her immediately.

0:12:20.800,0:12:21.680
Yes.

0:12:21.680,0:12:22.885
The Hall of Spring Joy?

0:12:23.480,0:12:25.248
How could she deserve such an honor？

0:12:25.680,0:12:26.720
Of course she does.

0:12:27.520,0:12:29.163
Based on the current situation,

0:12:29.720,0:12:32.000
I'm afraid that she will receive 
more promotions in the future.

0:12:33.400,0:12:34.855
Since she likes peace and quiet,

0:12:35.120,0:12:37.480
there's no quieter area than the Palace of Longevity.

0:12:38.080,0:12:40.520
I'll have her live under my nose

0:12:41.000,0:12:43.200
in case she plays any tricks.

0:13:02.280,0:13:03.396
There is no need.

0:13:03.396,0:13:04.360
Sit down.

0:13:11.160,0:13:12.364
What's wrong?

0:13:12.640,0:13:13.640
Are you upset?

0:13:14.720,0:13:16.477
Are you still not used to living here？

0:13:17.000,0:13:18.449
I'm like this wherever I live.

0:13:19.880,0:13:21.315
You've been here for days,

0:13:21.600,0:13:23.126
but I haven't seen you smile once.

0:13:24.680,0:13:26.600
If you feel constrained by life in the palace,

0:13:26.600,0:13:29.280
I'll take you to the Summer Palace 
for a visit when I have time.

0:13:29.480,0:13:31.280
Your Majesty is busy with state affairs.

0:13:31.680,0:13:33.120
There is no need to worry about me.

0:13:34.630,0:13:35.880
Besides, I don't smile...

0:13:36.800,0:13:38.645
because it is not in my nature.

0:13:41.278,0:13:42.484
There is no other reason.

0:13:47.800,0:13:50.000
You look even more beautiful when you're not smiling.

0:13:52.400,0:13:53.640
Your Majesty,

0:13:53.640,0:13:56.080
His Majesty really promoted 
a low-born girl to Companion?

0:13:58.200,0:13:59.283
Your Majesty,

0:13:59.800,0:14:01.724
according to the ancestors' rules,

0:14:01.724,0:14:03.560
a maid in the palace should be promoted to Escort first.

0:14:03.560,0:14:05.070
Ye Lanyi was not a maid.

0:14:05.080,0:14:06.720
Besides, His Majesty likes her.

0:14:06.720,0:14:08.165
There is nothing wrong with it.

0:14:08.404,0:14:09.920
The promotion ceremony was before noon,

0:14:09.920,0:14:11.320
she then accompanied His Majesty for dinner,

0:14:11.320,0:14:13.166
and served His Majesty that very night.

0:14:13.640,0:14:16.251
In the past few nights, His Majesty
has requested service only from her.

0:14:16.480,0:14:18.720
I have never seen His Majesty acting this way.

0:14:18.926,0:14:21.006
You haven't? Neither have I.

0:14:21.240,0:14:23.203
This is what's called "possessed by the devil".

0:14:23.760,0:14:25.880
Today, when I went to the Hall of
 Mental Cultivation to pay my respects,

0:14:25.880,0:14:27.844
I had a good look at Companion Ye.

0:14:28.360,0:14:30.393
Her attitude was arrogant and her manners rough.

0:14:30.640,0:14:32.444
I can't fathom what His Majesty likes about her.

0:14:33.320,0:14:35.323
Délice, if you are capable,

0:14:35.800,0:14:37.644
you can adopt her manners.

0:14:37.920,0:14:39.768
Then His Majesty would favor you just the same.

0:14:41.760,0:14:43.606
Ye has gained so much favor ...

0:14:43.606,0:14:44.931
It makes my heart quiver.

0:14:45.480,0:14:47.280
If she gives birth to a low-born scum someday ...

0:14:47.280,0:14:48.528
I can't imagine.

0:14:49.120,0:14:51.680
It would be a blessing from Heaven if she is barren.

0:15:40.000,0:15:41.083
Companion Ye.

0:15:43.720,0:15:44.720
Lord XVII.

0:15:47.076,0:15:48.246
You're here.

0:15:48.480,0:15:50.000
It's been a long time since we last met.

0:15:50.000,0:15:51.404
You've become a Companion now.

0:15:55.400,0:15:57.044
No one ever asked if I was willing

0:15:57.840,0:15:59.127
to be sent to the Palace,

0:15:59.760,0:16:01.088
or to become a Companion.

0:16:03.240,0:16:04.806
I heard about what happened to you.

0:16:05.560,0:16:06.770
You seem dispirited.

0:16:08.120,0:16:09.653
Everything here is filthy.

0:16:11.040,0:16:13.559
No place feels as pure as the stables at the Hundred Stallion Pavillion.

0:16:17.980,0:16:19.366
Do you remember that year

0:16:19.780,0:16:21.404
when you almost died from a high fever?

0:16:21.840,0:16:22.840
I remember.

0:16:24.000,0:16:25.406
It was seven years ago.

0:16:25.800,0:16:27.206
I was so sick and about to die.

0:16:27.560,0:16:29.724
Nobody cared about a humble servant like me.

0:16:30.320,0:16:32.175
But, by chance, Your Lordship saw me

0:16:32.640,0:16:34.165
and asked an imperial doctor to save me.

0:16:34.360,0:16:35.890
I didn't save you back then

0:16:35.890,0:16:38.220
to see you abandoning yourself to despair now.

0:16:38.580,0:16:40.226
But what else can I do?

