This is merely my wishful thinking.

0:19:36.880,0:19:38.489
It will never come to be.

0:19:42.080,0:19:43.080
Believe me.

0:19:43.760,0:19:45.480
When you fade from His Majesty’s memory,

0:19:45.480,0:19:47.686
I’ll ask Madam Abbess to report that you died of illness.

