The sooner you leave, the sooner you can return.

0:22:57.360,0:22:58.605
I shall take my leave.

0:23:05.652,0:23:06.640
Su Peisheng.

0:23:10.280,0:23:11.280
Your Majesty.

0:23:12.410,0:23:14.240
Summon Mr. Zhang Tingyu here.

0:23:14.725,0:23:15.720
Yes.

0:23:25.197,0:23:27.680
Peace to Your Majesty.

0:23:30.600,0:23:31.600
Please rise.

