I summoned you here

0:23:39.560,0:23:42.140
to discuss Noble Prince Guo's trip 
to Yunnan and Tibet.

0:23:43.360,0:23:46.850
You need to send reliable people 
to protect him carefully and covertly.

0:23:47.560,0:23:48.560
Also,

0:23:49.450,0:23:52.883
to prevent Noble Prince Guo from 
unduly interfering with state affairs.

0:23:53.800,0:23:55.045
Wherever he goes,

0:23:55.600,0:23:56.920
whoever he talks to,

0:23:57.240,0:23:58.410
whatever he does,

0:23:59.000,0:24:00.796
must be carefully observed

0:24:00.796,0:24:02.778
and reported back in a timely manner.

0:24:03.300,0:24:04.280
Yes.

0:24:15.720,0:24:16.720
Dr. Wen.

0:24:17.720,0:24:18.885
Is the formula ready?

0:24:21.800,0:24:22.883
Yes, it is.

0:24:29.838,0:24:30.948
Be careful when using it.

0:24:33.880,0:24:34.880
Thank you.

0:24:36.000,0:24:37.083
Don't thank me.

0:24:38.370,0:24:41.120
I just don't want Huan'er
to suffer in an abyss of misery.

0:24:43.000,0:24:44.253
I still want to thank you.

0:24:57.120,0:24:58.722
Why were you so careless 
when dismounting the horse?

0:24:59.400,0:25:01.428
Now there is a hole in your cloak.

0:25:02.110,0:25:03.600
I haven't seen you for four days,

0:25:04.174,0:25:05.384
so I rushed off the horse.

0:25:06.360,0:25:07.600
It's only a cloak,

0:25:07.600,0:25:08.765
nothing precious.

0:25:09.200,0:25:10.843
The mountain roads are difficult on snowy days,

0:25:11.038,0:25:12.560
and horses can easily slip.

0:25:12.800,0:25:14.468
You didn't have to come here so hurriedly.

0:25:15.720,0:25:17.146
It's your cloak this time.

0:25:17.400,0:25:19.360
But the next time, you could hurt yourself.

0:25:20.000,0:25:21.800
Are you deliberately trying to worry me?

0:25:21.880,0:25:23.211
I promise to be careful next time.

0:25:23.800,0:25:25.440
I don't want to injure myself either.

0:25:25.960,0:25:27.260
If I was injured,

0:25:27.260,0:25:28.648
how could I come to see you?

0:25:29.760,0:25:30.880
Such a glib tongue.

0:25:34.310,0:25:35.673
If your clothes are torn again,

0:25:35.840,0:25:37.893
there won't be anyone to mend them for you.

0:25:38.880,0:25:41.044
I don't care if you walk around in tattered clothes.

0:25:45.080,0:25:46.324
Are you leaving tomorrow?

0:25:46.920,0:25:49.120
It's already the 23rd of the last lunar month.

0:25:49.720,0:25:50.720
I can't delay any longer.

0:25:50.830,0:25:52.605
No matter what, I can't be in Beijing for New Year.

0:25:53.168,0:25:54.378
You will be back in forty days?

0:25:54.403,0:25:55.480
Within forty days,

0:25:55.480,0:25:56.769
I will definitely be back.

0:25:58.040,0:25:59.040
Forty days...

0:26:00.360,0:26:02.080
The moon will be full once again.

0:26:02.380,0:26:03.648
The days will fly by.

0:26:04.520,0:26:05.960
I have everything arranged.

0:26:05.960,0:26:07.120
After I come back,

0:26:07.280,0:26:08.675
I will take you away from here.

0:26:08.840,0:26:09.840
Really?

0:26:15.600,0:26:16.600
This is...?

0:26:16.600,0:26:17.600
Look.

0:26:23.720,0:26:24.800
It looks like makeup powder.

0:26:25.261,0:26:26.600
Dr. Wen prepared this medicine

0:26:26.600,0:26:27.885
 for you to feign death.

0:26:28.650,0:26:30.020
It's called the Seven-Day Sedate.

0:26:30.462,0:26:31.886
Made from jimsonweed.

0:26:32.280,0:26:33.337
After taking it,

0:26:33.680,0:26:35.323
your breathing will pause

0:26:35.920,0:26:37.182
as if you were dead.

0:26:38.040,0:26:39.171
Seven days later,

0:26:40.000,0:26:41.160
you will regain consciousness.

0:26:42.800,0:26:44.320
He is willing to help me after all.

0:26:45.720,0:26:46.782
Dr. Wen ...

0:26:46.782,0:26:48.526
has put so much thought into helping us.

0:26:49.000,0:26:50.405
We must thank him profusely.

0:26:52.720,0:26:54.256
I have arranged everything for our plan.

0:26:54.560,0:26:55.880
After my obligations are fulfilled,

0:26:56.520,0:26:57.520
Huan'er,

0:26:58.400,0:26:59.480
at that time,

0:27:00.000,0:27:01.481
we will be together forever.

0:27:02.200,0:27:03.400
When you come back

0:27:03.400,0:27:04.520
and everything is complete,

0:27:05.240,0:27:06.770
I will truly be able to put my mind at ease.

0:27:07.800,0:27:08.875
Huan'er,

0:27:09.040,0:27:10.448
this is of particular concern to the state.

0:27:10.800,0:27:11.883
I have to go.

0:27:13.080,0:27:14.120
It's only forty days.

0:27:14.720,0:27:16.048
I will be here waiting for you.

