Back in the day,

0:27:21.200,0:27:22.846
an aunt from the south told me that

0:27:23.600,0:27:25.500
there is a bridge by West Lake in Hangzhou.

0:27:25.920,0:27:27.000
It is called the Long Bridge.

0:27:27.920,0:27:29.124
The Long Bridge?

0:27:30.920,0:27:32.000
Is the bridge very long?

0:27:32.760,0:27:34.040
Actually, it is not long.

0:27:34.920,0:27:36.160
It's called the Long Bridge

0:27:36.720,0:27:38.480
because the local people say that

0:27:38.720,0:27:40.320
Liang Shanbo and Zhu Yingtai

0:27:40.400,0:27:41.883
made their farewells on the bridge.

0:27:42.320,0:27:43.965
Because they were reluctant to part,

0:27:44.160,0:27:47.000
the short bridge felt very long to cross over.

0:27:48.760,0:27:50.320
The grief and sorrow of parting

0:27:50.320,0:27:51.720
has been the same

0:27:51.920,0:27:53.120
from ancient times to now.

0:27:53.560,0:27:55.240
I don't want to be like them.

