Zhu's father betrothed her to another,

0:27:57.080,0:27:58.662
The news caused Liang to vomit blood and die.

0:27:58.942,0:28:00.787
Their spirits turned into butterflies 
to fly away from this world.

0:28:01.320,0:28:02.880
We are much luckier than them.

0:28:05.400,0:28:06.737
It was a mistake ...

0:28:06.737,0:28:08.000
to compare us to them.

0:28:11.080,0:28:12.480
I'm irrationally anxious these days,

0:28:12.880,0:28:14.283
and can't bear to hear ill-fated stories.

0:28:16.080,0:28:17.800
It is evident that once a man

0:28:18.200,0:28:20.080
holds his love dear to his heart,

0:28:21.560,0:28:22.920
he can no longer be carefree.

0:28:24.840,0:28:26.146
Go and be as carefree as you wish.

0:28:26.680,0:28:28.180
Noble Prince Guo has always been 
talented and unrestrained.

0:28:28.680,0:28:30.440
There is no need to worry about 
a lack of beautiful women

0:28:30.440,0:28:31.885
delivering themselves to you.

0:28:36.560,0:28:37.667
What's the matter with you?

0:28:37.667,0:28:38.680
I was only joking,

0:28:38.720,0:28:39.800
yet you get so mean to me.

0:28:40.280,0:28:41.800
You must be mad because I was right.

0:28:42.080,0:28:43.324
You deserved it for talking nonsense.

0:28:48.120,0:28:50.000
Even though the flowers will beckon you on the road,

0:28:50.000,0:28:51.600
please come back as speedily as possible.

0:28:52.560,0:28:53.560
Because...

0:28:53.800,0:28:55.124
I will be waiting for you here.

0:28:56.000,0:28:57.010
With you here,

0:28:58.720,0:29:00.408
my heart will want to return like a shooting arrow.

0:29:43.720,0:29:44.720
Huan'er.

0:29:50.120,0:29:51.120
Huan'er.

0:30:05.320,0:30:06.320
Huan'er.

0:30:17.920,0:30:19.000
I will come back soon.

0:30:19.400,0:30:20.520
I will be waiting for you.

0:30:27.000,0:30:28.000
Please do.

0:30:43.920,0:30:45.320
I will be waiting for you!

0:31:02.840,0:31:04.010
I will wait for you.

