My Lady,

0:31:29.480,0:31:31.840
I have sent the winter coats to Anqi Temple
as you asked.

0:31:32.720,0:31:34.670
Her Venerable Highness sent her regards.

0:31:34.680,0:31:35.799
She also said that

0:31:35.799,0:31:37.200
His Lordship will come back soon

0:31:37.200,0:31:39.800
and you should visit her together upon his return.

0:31:40.520,0:31:42.075
I've been feeling fatigued recently

0:31:42.075,0:31:43.360
and don't want to walk around.

0:31:44.120,0:31:46.520
But Yunli will be back within ten days at most.

0:31:47.200,0:31:49.000
I will wait for him, and visit 
Her Venerable Highness together.

0:31:51.720,0:31:53.044
Prioress Mochou,

0:31:53.160,0:31:54.885
a distinguished guest from the palace is here.

0:31:58.080,0:31:59.160
Meizhuang!

0:31:59.480,0:32:00.480
Huan'er!

0:32:01.280,0:32:02.557
It's my fault

0:32:02.557,0:32:04.200
for not visiting you until today.

0:32:04.400,0:32:05.400
Let's sit down.

0:32:10.500,0:32:13.093
Finally, we manage to 
meet this once after so many years.

0:32:13.093,0:32:14.200
Let's cry no more!

0:32:19.000,0:32:20.346
For no good reason,

0:32:20.346,0:32:23.000
how could you place my sister 
in such a remote residence?

0:32:23.960,0:32:25.753
I came from Temple of Pure Dew

0:32:25.753,0:32:27.880
and it took an hour even on the sedan.

0:32:28.544,0:32:32.140
Is this how the temple takes care of concubines
who practice Buddhism outside the palace?

