I was sick a while back,

0:32:35.480,0:32:37.010
so I moved here to recuperate.

0:32:37.400,0:32:39.010
It has nothing to do with Madam Abbess.

0:32:39.040,0:32:40.885
Mochou, it's very kind of you to say so.

0:32:41.280,0:32:42.280
Yes, yes.

0:32:42.600,0:32:45.200
Mochou moved here because she was sick.

0:32:47.149,0:32:48.719
All of you, wait outside.

0:32:48.920,0:32:51.080
I wish to speak with Mochou privately.

0:32:52.200,0:32:53.200
Yes, Your Highness.

0:32:53.320,0:32:54.765
Everyone can go,

0:32:54.880,0:32:56.800
but Prioress Jingbai is fit and strong.

0:32:57.245,0:33:00.330
I ask her to clear the snow off the road
to ease my return to the palace.

0:33:00.920,0:33:03.000
To show your respect for Her Highness Concubine Vertu,

0:33:03.000,0:33:04.772
please finish it on your own, Prioress.

0:33:06.480,0:33:07.480
Yes.

0:33:12.160,0:33:13.920
Why did you ask her to do that?

0:33:14.800,0:33:17.606
You have endured so much in the Temple of Pure Dew.

0:33:19.800,0:33:20.800
Not really.

0:33:21.160,0:33:22.650
You still try to hide it from me.

0:33:22.800,0:33:24.448
You think I don't know?

0:33:24.880,0:33:27.520
You were sent here after being banished
from the palace.

0:33:28.120,0:33:31.040
Everyone in this world treads on those
who are lower in status.

0:33:31.400,0:33:33.910
Even people in a Buddhist temple
can have worldly dispositions.

0:33:35.435,0:33:37.280
When I asked to visit you just now,

0:33:37.280,0:33:39.400
Jingbai tried hard to refuse me,

0:33:39.400,0:33:41.645
saying the weather was cold and the road slippery.

0:33:42.160,0:33:44.170
We barely exchanged words and

0:33:44.170,0:33:45.920
she was already showing her guilty conscience.

0:33:45.920,0:33:47.965
It's obvious that she bullies you frequently.

0:33:48.800,0:33:50.560
I punished her in your presence,

0:33:51.080,0:33:52.883
not only to teach her a lesson,

0:33:52.883,0:33:55.720
but also to show her you weren't the one
responsible for her punishment,

0:33:55.720,0:33:57.606
so she won't retaliate against you later.

0:33:57.920,0:33:59.485
It's very thoughtful of you.

0:34:00.200,0:34:01.524
It's all right, all right.

0:34:01.720,0:34:03.560
I was worried that you suffered greatly.

0:34:04.048,0:34:07.200
