terribly sick and moved away.

0:34:07.760,0:34:10.248
I was so scared all the way here.

0:34:11.400,0:34:13.400
Seeing you in good health,

0:34:14.400,0:34:16.124
I feel some relief now.

0:34:19.000,0:34:20.684
I heard you were promoted 
to the rank of Concubine.

0:34:20.880,0:34:22.648
I was happy for so many days.

0:34:23.840,0:34:25.210
What's the use of that?

0:34:25.400,0:34:27.400
I don't care about rank or titles.

0:34:29.200,0:34:30.920
Why would you think like that?

0:34:32.122,0:34:33.360
For the past two years,

0:34:33.360,0:34:35.489
His Majesty has been very hard on himself.

0:34:35.800,0:34:37.600
He buried himself in work.

0:34:38.360,0:34:39.480
Since you left,

0:34:39.600,0:34:42.240
His Majesty has been cold towards the harem.

0:34:43.400,0:34:45.190
In addition to Concubine Délice,

0:34:45.200,0:34:47.880
His Majesty has newly favored
Concubine Fidèle and Attendant Kang.

0:34:48.760,0:34:49.920
But it is hard to tell

0:34:50.000,0:34:52.005
who he truly adores in the harem.

0:34:52.440,0:34:53.760
It didn't become better until

0:34:53.760,0:34:55.885
Companion Ye entered the palace several days ago.

0:34:56.680,0:34:59.160
Nowadays, His Majesty treats me 
with simple courtesy.

0:34:59.920,0:35:01.136
It's for the best.

0:35:01.320,0:35:03.040
With the rank of Concubine,

0:35:03.040,0:35:05.920
I can take more liberty with certain things.

0:35:06.640,0:35:09.000
Madam Orchid can often visit me -

0:35:09.320,0:35:11.406
because you spoke on my behalf with 
the Empress Dowager.

0:35:12.320,0:35:13.720
You have done so much for me...

0:35:13.720,0:35:15.080
If I were the one suffering,

0:35:15.400,0:35:17.280
you would have done the same for me.

0:35:18.520,0:35:19.520
Huan'er,

0:35:19.600,0:35:20.930
I took your advice

0:35:21.000,0:35:22.879
and "blunted my sharp thorn" in the harem

0:35:23.120,0:35:24.925
to avoid attracting the Empress’s attention.

0:35:25.570,0:35:27.800
I devoted myself to serving the Empress Dowager

0:35:27.800,0:35:29.760
and taking care of Longyue with Consort Estime.

0:35:30.360,0:35:31.400
So one day ...

0:35:31.400,0:35:34.880
I can help redress all the injustices 
done to you, in a single blow.

0:35:35.990,0:35:37.560
However, after so many years,

0:35:37.560,0:35:39.720
I still haven’t gathered much useful evidence.

0:35:43.400,0:35:44.938
It’s hard to get out of the palace,

0:35:44.938,0:35:46.209
especially in the first lunar month.

0:35:46.680,0:35:48.205
How did you manage to come out?

0:35:49.920,0:35:51.720
Princess Wenyi fell sick several days ago.

0:35:52.240,0:35:53.800
Although the doctors have been treating her,

0:35:53.800,0:35:57.280
the exorcist from the Baohua Hall
said she's haunted by spirits of the dead.

0:35:57.280,0:36:01.186
So, we must move the caskets of any concubine
 who had a sudden demise, here to the temple.

0:36:01.480,0:36:03.360
But it’s inauspicious to undertake this task

0:36:03.387,0:36:04.849
in the first lunar month.

0:36:05.120,0:36:06.448
Why was it assigned to you?

0:36:07.000,0:36:08.200
The exorcist said that

0:36:08.200,0:36:10.680
only someone who hasn't been intimate 
with His Majesty for a long time

0:36:10.680,0:36:13.086
can fulfill such commitment that requires 
physical and spiritual purity.

0:36:13.560,0:36:14.560
Of course,

0:36:14.560,0:36:16.640
I'm not the only concubine who fits the description.

0:36:17.200,0:36:19.405
But other concubines considered it bad luck.

0:36:19.680,0:36:21.280
So it fell to me.

0:36:22.400,0:36:24.486
You have always been cautious 
in matters related to death.

0:36:25.000,0:36:27.880
Normally, you would never get involved in
rituals for redeeming lost souls.

0:36:29.680,0:36:30.680
Meizhuang,

0:36:31.440,0:36:34.080
did you really come to the temple
to guide these souls to the Pure Land,

0:36:34.080,0:36:35.930
or it was an excuse to visit me?

0:36:38.920,0:36:40.400
Given your insightfulness,

0:36:40.560,0:36:42.049
I won’t hide it from you anymore.

0:36:42.760,0:36:44.008
I asked Wen Shichu

0:36:44.008,0:36:46.006
to medicate Princess Wenyi to induce a fever.

0:36:46.400,0:36:48.240
And I bribed the exorcist in the Baohua Hall

0:36:48.240,0:36:49.560
to suggest the ritual.

0:36:50.080,0:36:53.000
All for having a chance to come see you.

0:36:53.120,0:36:54.608
You went to such painstaking efforts...

0:36:55.080,0:36:56.765
It must be something serious.

0:36:57.520,0:36:58.880
Did something happen to Longyue?

0:36:58.880,0:37:00.760
No, no, not Longyue.

0:37:00.920,0:37:01.955
She is good.

0:37:01.955,0:37:03.160
Nothing happened to her.

0:37:04.880,0:37:05.880
It is…

0:37:07.160,0:37:08.400
It is your father.

0:37:08.760,0:37:10.249
He fell gravely ill in Ningguta,

0:37:10.249,0:37:11.623
his life is in critical condition.

0:37:15.600,0:37:16.920
My father was healthy...

0:37:18.600,0:37:20.000
How did he become gravely ill?

0:37:20.040,0:37:21.000
Yes...

0:37:21.000,0:37:22.320
Even though your father was exiled,

0:37:22.320,0:37:23.880
he had been in good health.

0:37:24.680,0:37:26.320
I hesitated for days

0:37:26.320,0:37:27.760
if I should tell you.

0:37:28.520,0:37:29.840
I was afraid that the news would

0:37:29.840,0:37:31.525
overwhelm you with sadness.

0:37:32.360,0:37:33.360
But…

0:37:33.720,0:37:35.435
after turning it over in my mind,

0:37:35.640,0:37:37.478
I am more worried for your father's life.

0:37:37.720,0:37:39.640
I had to come and tell you.

0:37:40.080,0:37:41.655
My father was perfectly healthy.

0:37:42.960,0:37:44.400
What exactly happened?

0:37:45.000,0:37:46.660
That's my question too.

0:37:47.000,0:37:48.890
There is nothing we can do if it was Heaven's will.

0:37:49.400,0:37:51.200
But if someone deliberately harmed him ...

0:37:51.200,0:37:53.006
That would be truly terrifying.

0:37:53.320,0:37:54.380
Do you think...

0:37:55.560,0:37:57.000
it's a premeditated act?

0:37:58.040,0:38:00.640
I suspect that the Empress did something in secret.

0:38:01.520,0:38:02.520
Or ...

0:38:02.520,0:38:04.880
it could be Concubine Délice‘s family -
outside of the palace.

0:38:04.880,0:38:06.630
I never thought that after all this time,

0:38:06.920,0:38:08.960
they would still hound your family relentlessly.

0:38:09.960,0:38:11.800
The Zhen family has been exiled to Ningguta.

0:38:12.320,0:38:13.995
And I left the palace to practice in a nunnery.

0:38:14.160,0:38:16.445
Why are they still persecuting us?

0:38:16.760,0:38:17.777
Huan’er,

0:38:17.777,0:38:19.723
now is not the time to feel aggrieved.

0:38:20.600,0:38:21.990
Your father was plotted against.

0:38:22.280,0:38:25.233
Who knows if you will be their next target?

0:38:26.120,0:38:27.620
You have to find a way

0:38:27.620,0:38:29.480
to bring your father back to Beijing 
for medical care as soon as possible.

0:38:29.800,0:38:32.320
Perhaps he can recover with proper care.

0:38:33.360,0:38:34.360
You are right.

0:38:35.640,0:38:36.640
For the time being,

0:38:37.640,0:38:39.080
his life is the most important.

0:38:40.640,0:38:42.050
As for treating my father,

0:38:42.520,0:38:44.400
I will try my best to come up with a way.

0:38:44.400,0:38:45.400
Yes.

0:38:48.360,0:38:50.080
Your Highness, it's time to go.

0:38:50.080,0:38:51.845
We have to return to the palace before dark.

0:38:52.200,0:38:53.400
I understand.

0:38:53.680,0:38:55.000
Ask the carriage to wait.

0:38:55.520,0:38:57.520
Yes, Your Highness, but please don't be long.

0:38:58.080,0:38:59.080
Huan'er,

0:39:00.520,0:39:01.644
I have to leave now.

0:39:02.400,0:39:04.030
Just remember this for me:

0:39:04.640,0:39:05.920
preserving yourself

0:39:06.480,0:39:07.840
is the most important.

0:39:11.360,0:39:12.565
The palace is a dangerous place.

0:39:14.240,0:39:15.520
You need to be careful as well.

0:39:17.160,0:39:18.415
I don't know when...

0:39:20.040,0:39:21.760
we will be able to see each other again.

0:39:23.200,0:39:25.089
As long as we are both safe and healthy,

0:39:25.600,0:39:27.242
it doesn't matter

0:39:27.242,0:39:29.006
whether we get to see each other or not.

0:39:38.480,0:39:39.728
Do take care of yourself.

0:39:42.000,0:39:43.000
You as well.

0:40:16.120,0:40:18.000
How come Mistress skipped dinner again?

0:40:19.320,0:40:20.763
Mr. Zhen is not well.

0:40:21.120,0:40:22.560
I am very worried, too.

0:40:25.080,0:40:26.940
I hope His Lordship can return soon.

0:40:27.600,0:40:29.165
He would be able to help us out.

0:40:34.120,0:40:35.330
Mistress, what's wrong?

0:40:36.280,0:40:37.728
Is it something you ate?

0:40:43.600,0:40:44.600
Are you...

0:40:47.060,0:40:48.305
Congratulations, Mistress!

0:40:49.200,0:40:50.612
It has been less than a month.

0:40:50.612,0:40:51.724
Keep your voice down.

0:40:53.000,0:40:54.560
You should inform Consort Dowager.

0:40:54.560,0:40:56.006
She will be elated to hear the news.

0:40:57.000,0:40:58.920
I just learned about my father's illness.

0:40:58.920,0:41:00.320
I'm not in the mood for a celebration.

0:41:02.200,0:41:03.685
I'll wait untill Yunli is back,

0:41:04.480,0:41:05.926
and we can tell Consort Dowager together.

0:41:11.880,0:41:12.880
Jade.

0:41:18.120,0:41:19.320
The child in my belly ...

0:41:19.600,0:41:20.926
is going to call you auntie.

0:41:23.570,0:41:24.814
Yurao and our parents

0:41:24.814,0:41:26.240
are far away in Ningguta.

0:41:27.360,0:41:28.520
I'm afraid that

0:41:28.720,0:41:30.926
we can only depend on each other 
for the rest of our lives.

0:41:32.600,0:41:34.430
My child is also your child.

0:41:35.680,0:41:36.920
From now on,

0:41:37.400,0:41:38.720
we'll raise him together.

0:41:39.440,0:41:40.440
Shall we?

0:41:41.880,0:41:42.880
Really?

0:41:48.000,0:41:49.765
The child of you and His Lordship,

0:41:51.320,0:41:52.573
is also my child.

0:41:54.920,0:41:55.920
Jade.

0:41:57.560,0:41:59.616
Like the placement of stones at the end of a Go game,

0:41:59.616,0:42:00.812
some things are irreversible.

0:42:01.480,0:42:02.680
Trying to change such things

0:42:02.680,0:42:04.284
will only hurt yourself and others.

0:42:05.760,0:42:07.278
But I promise I will give you

0:42:07.800,0:42:09.164
everything I can.

0:42:11.720,0:42:12.720
I understand.

0:42:13.880,0:42:15.003
Some things...

0:42:15.520,0:42:16.844
are not fated in life.

0:42:18.200,0:42:19.680
They cannot be forced to happen.

